#### Rough Design Sketch.

Sketch via [tinkercad](https://www.tinkercad.com). Two lighting points, two of triple double gang sockets (with built in USB) and a doubel docket to power the telly.  Planning to use easybulb.com / limitlessled.com/ / mi-light to control the lights - hence no physical wired lighting switches. 

~~At the moment the limiting factor is the 6A MCB on my house's consumer unit that [feeds outside](https://imgur.com/a/RQNy2).~~

Items to purchase:-
* http://www.screwfix.com/p/time-arctic-flexible-cable-3183ag-3-core-2-5mm-x-50m-blue/94475
* http://www.screwfix.com/p/tower-round-cable-clips-9-10mm-white-pack-of-100/11824
* http://www.screwfix.com/p/tower-external-gland-kit-20-ip66-pack-of-2/56505
* http://www.screwfix.com/p/-/44635

Within the walls
